      "id": "post-1780663113659",
      "title": "Fail Safe Logic",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-05",
      "category": "General",
      "tags": [
        "Fail Safe"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/Fail%20Safe.jpeg",
      "excerpt": "Fail Safe Logic in each project often not goes to advance level.",
      "content": "<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p> In almost all the project, fail safe design and logic is given less importance and carried out only for customer satisfaction.\nAny Fail Safe logic must have details like which Safety Category has been adopted, how it is designed and how it is going to be executed. \nCustomer will be more curious and will realize how serious are we about safety.\nWiring E-Stop to safety relay or PLC often goes with theory logic.\nThis must be analyzed in detail, designer need to adopt a system to understand what type of safety ,customer requires or if he is not aware, based on project 3D CAD needs to present safety category adopted in design.\n</p>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Github2drb/Controls_Team_Tracker/main/blog-images/Fail%20Safe.jpeg\" \n     style=\"width:100%; border-radius:8px; margin:12px 0;\" />",
      "isPinned": true,
      "isPublished": true,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-05T12:38:33.659Z"
    },
    {
      "id": "post-1782194326819",
      "title": "Controls Project Allocation & Assignment",
      "author": "Admin",
      "date": "2026-06-23",
      "category": "General",
      "tags": [
        "#Project_Assignment_Matrix"
      ],
      "coverImage": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1716191300020-b52dec5b70a8?w=1600&q=80&fit=crop",
      "excerpt": "Dynamic project allocation template with engineer selection from GitHub. Assign team members, dates, and tasks. Download filled forms for approval and signatures",
      "content": "<!-- CONTROLS PROJECT FORM - SELF-CONTAINED (NO EXTERNAL JS NEEDED) -->\n<style>\n.cpf-container{max-width:900px;margin:20px auto;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background:#fff;padding:20px;border:1px solid #ddd}\n.cpf-header{background:#667eea;color:#fff;padding:20px;border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:25px}\n.cpf-header h2{margin:0;font-size:22px}\n.cpf-section{background:#f9f9f9;border-left:4px solid #667eea;padding:15px;margin-bottom:15px}\n.cpf-section h3{color:#003366;font-size:14px;margin:0 0 10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;padding-bottom:5px}\n.cpf-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px}\n.cpf-grid.full{grid-template-columns:1fr}\n.cpf-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n.cpf-group label{font-size:11px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:4px;color:#555}\n.cpf-group input,.cpf-group select{padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%}\n.cpf-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;font-size:10px}\n.cpf-table th{background:#e8e8e8;padding:8px;border:1px solid #ddd;font-weight:bold}\n.cpf-table td{padding:6px;border:1px solid #ddd}\n.cpf-table input{width:100%;padding:4px;border:1px solid #ddd;box-sizing:border-box}\n.cpf-checkbox-group{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin:8px 0}\n.cpf-checkbox-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:11px}\n.cpf-checkbox-item input{width:14px;height:14px;cursor:pointer}\n.cpf-buttons{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:20px 0;justify-content:center}\n.cpf-btn{padding:12px 24px;border:none;border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;font-weight:bold;font-size:13px;transition:all .2s}\n.cpf-btn:active{transform:scale(0.98)}\n.cpf-btn-save{background:#4caf50;color:#fff}\n.cpf-btn-save:hover{background:#45a049}\n.cpf-btn-pdf{background:#2196f3;color:#fff}\n.cpf-btn-pdf:hover{background:#0b7dda}\n.cpf-btn-reset{background:#f0f0f0;color:#666;border:1px solid #ccc}\n.cpf-status{padding:12px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;display:none;font-weight:bold;border:1px solid;animation:slideDown 0.3s ease}\n.cpf-status.success{background:#d4edda;color:#155724;border-color:#c3e6cb}\n.cpf-status.error{background:#f8d7da;color:#721c24;border-color:#f5c6cb}\n.cpf-status.show{display:block}\n@keyframes slideDown{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"cpf-container\" id=\"cpfContainer\">\n  <div class=\"cpf-header\">\n    <h2>⚙️ Controls Project Allocation & Assignment</h2>\n    <p>Fill form and save or download</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div id=\"cpfStatus\" class=\"cpf-status\"></div>\n\n  <form id=\"cpfForm\" name=\"cpfForm\">\n    \n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>1. Project Overview</h3>\n      <div class=\"cpf-grid\">\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Name</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_projectName\" placeholder=\"Name\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Code</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_projectCode\" placeholder=\"Code\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Client/Facility</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_client\" placeholder=\"Client\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Project Manager</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_projectManager\" placeholder=\"PM\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Start Date</label>\n          <input type=\"date\" id=\"f_startDate\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Completion Date</label>\n          <input type=\"date\" id=\"f_completionDate\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Budget</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_budget\" placeholder=\"Amount\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Priority</label>\n          <select id=\"f_priority\">\n            <option>Select</option>\n            <option>Critical</option>\n            <option>High</option>\n            <option>Medium</option>\n            <option>Low</option>\n          </select>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"cpf-group cpf-grid full\">\n        <label style=\"font-weight:bold\">Project Type</label>\n        <div class=\"cpf-checkbox-group\">\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_projType\" value=\"New Installation\"> New Installation</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_projType\" value=\"Retrofit\"> Retrofit</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_projType\" value=\"Maintenance\"> Maintenance</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_projType\" value=\"Upgrade\"> Upgrade</label>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"cpf-group cpf-grid full\">\n        <label style=\"font-weight:bold\">Safety Classification</label>\n        <div class=\"cpf-checkbox-group\">\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"f_safety\" value=\"Standard\"> Standard</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"f_safety\" value=\"High Risk\"> High Risk</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"f_safety\" value=\"Confined Space\"> Confined Space</label>\n          <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"radio\" name=\"f_safety\" value=\"Hot Work\"> Hot Work</label>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>2. Project Scope & Systems</h3>\n      <label style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:11px\">Automation Systems</label>\n      <div class=\"cpf-checkbox-group\">\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"PLC Programming\"> PLC Programming</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"HMI/SCADA\"> HMI/SCADA</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"Motor Control\"> Motor Control</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"Instrumentation\"> Instrumentation</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"Industrial Networks\"> Industrial Networks</label>\n        <label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"f_systems\" value=\"Safety Systems\"> Safety Systems</label>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>3. Team Assignment Matrix</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Team Member</th><th>Role</th><th>Tasks</th><th>Hours</th><th>Start</th><th>End</th></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n        <tr><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><input type=\"number\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td><td><input type=\"date\"></td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>4. Skill Requirements</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Certification</th><th>Team Member</th><th>Status</th></tr>\n        <tr><td>PLC Programming</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>HMI Development</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Industrial Safety</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n        <tr><td>Electrical Installation</td><td><input type=\"text\"></td><td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Verified</label></td></tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>8. Risk Assessment & Mitigation</h3>\n      <table class=\"cpf-table\">\n        <tr><th>Risk Factor</th><th>Probability</th><th>Impact</th><th>Mitigation</th></tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Equipment Delivery Delays</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Site Access Restrictions</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Technical Skill Gaps</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td>Safety Incidents</td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Low</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> Medium</label><label class=\"cpf-checkbox-item\" style=\"margin:0\"><input type=\"checkbox\"> High</label></td>\n          <td><input type=\"text\"></td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-section\">\n      <h3>Document Information</h3>\n      <div class=\"cpf-grid\">\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Prepared By</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_preparedBy\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"cpf-group\">\n          <label>Approved By</label>\n          <input type=\"text\" id=\"f_approvedBy\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"cpf-buttons\">\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-save\" id=\"cpfBtnSave\">💾 Save Locally</button>\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-pdf\" id=\"cpfBtnDownload\">📥 Download PDF</button>\n      <button type=\"reset\" class=\"cpf-btn cpf-btn-reset\">🔄 Reset</button>\n    </div>\n  </form>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n(function() {\n  var form = document.getElementById('cpfForm');\n  var btnSave = document.getElementById('cpfBtnSave');\n  var btnDownload = document.getElementById('cpfBtnDownload');\n  var statusEl = document.getElementById('cpfStatus');\n\n  function show(msg, type) {\n    statusEl.textContent = msg;\n    statusEl.className = 'cpf-status ' + type + ' show';\n    setTimeout(function() { statusEl.className = 'cpf-status'; }, 4000);\n  }\n\n  function getAllFormData() {\n    var data = {};\n    var fields = form.querySelectorAll('input, select, textarea');\n    fields.forEach(function(f) {\n      var k = f.id || f.name || 'f_' + Math.random();\n      if (f.type === 'checkbox' || f.type === 'radio') {\n        if (f.checked) data[k] = f.value;\n      } else if (f.value) {\n        data[k] = f.value;\n      }\n    });\n    return data;\n  }\n\n  btnSave.onclick = function(e) {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    try {\n      var code = document.getElementById('f_projectCode').value || 'Project';\n      var name = document.getElementById('f_projectName').value || 'Unnamed';\n      \n      if (!code.trim()) {\n        show('❌ Please enter Project Code', 'error');\n        return;\n      }\n\n      var obj = {\n        code: code,\n        name: name,\n        date: new Date().toLocaleString(),\n        data: getAllFormData()\n      };\n\n      var key = 'cpf_' + code.replace(/\\s/g, '_') + '_' + Date.now();\n      localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(obj));\n      localStorage.setItem('cpf_last_' + code, JSON.stringify(obj));\n      \n      show('✅ Saved: ' + name + ' (' + code + ')', 'success');\n    } catch (err) {\n      show('❌ Error: ' + err.message, 'error');\n    }\n  };\n\n  btnDownload.onclick = function(e) {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    try {\n      var code = document.getElementById('f_projectCode').value || 'Project';\n      var name = document.getElementById('f_projectName').value || 'Unnamed';\n      \n      if (!code.trim()) {\n        show('❌ Please enter Project Code', 'error');\n        return;\n      }\n\n      var html = '<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><title>' + code + '</title><style>body{font-family:Arial;margin:20px;color:#333}h1{color:#667eea;border-bottom:3px solid;padding:10px 0;margin-bottom:10px}h2{color:#003366;font-size:14px;margin-top:15px}table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;font-size:11px}th,td{border:1px solid #ddd;padding:8px;text-align:left}th{background:#f0f0f0}.section{page-break-inside:avoid}@media print{body{margin:0}}</style></head><body>';\n      html += '<h1>' + code + ' - ' + name + '</h1>';\n      html += '<p><strong>Date:</strong> ' + new Date().toLocaleDateString() + '</p>';\n      html += document.getElementById('cpfContainer').innerHTML;\n      html += '</body></html>';\n\n      var blob = new Blob([html], { type: 'text/html' });\n      var url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);\n      var link = document.createElement('a');\n      link.href = url;\n      link.download = code.replace(/\\s/g, '_') + '.html';\n      document.body.appendChild(link);\n      link.click();\n      document.body.removeChild(link);\n      URL.revokeObjectURL(url);\n\n      show('✅ Downloaded. Open file → Print → Save as PDF', 'success');\n    } catch (err) {\n      show('❌ Error: ' + err.message, 'error');\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Load saved data\n  window.addEventListener('load', function() {\n    try {\n      var code = document.getElementById('f_projectCode').value;\n      if (code) {\n        var saved = localStorage.getItem('cpf_last_' + code);\n        if (saved) {\n          var obj = JSON.parse(saved);\n          for (var k in obj.data) {\n            var f = document.getElementById(k) || form.querySelector('[name=\"' + k + '\"]');\n            if (f) f.value = obj.data[k];\n          }\n          show('📝 Data restored', 'success');\n        }\n      }\n    } catch (e) {}\n  });\n\n  console.log('✅ CPF Form Ready - Buttons Working');\n})();\n</script>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "isPublished": true,
      "createdAt": "2026-06-23T05:58:46.819Z"
    },
